law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 196, sec. 34. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 172, sec. 4. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 13. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 184, secs. 3 and 11. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3990e-5.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Commission to furnish pocket card to each licensee.
